OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,FA dad whose baby spent his first 10
OL,7,Fdays in intensive care, has urged the
OL,8,Fgovernment to increase the statutory
OL,9,Ftwo-week paternity leave.
OL,11,FScott Ramage from Walkden in Salford,
OL,12,Fcalled the leave entitlement
OL,13,F'inadequate' and said the UK has
OL,14,FEurope's worst paternity leave.
OL,16,FIt comes as new research shows almost
OL,17,Fhalf of new fathers experience
OL,18,Fmultiple symptoms of depression and
OL,19,Fanxiety in their baby's first year.
