OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,FWhen Scott's son Tyler was born two
OL,7,Fyears ago, he became dangerously ill
OL,8,Fwith sepsis and spent 10 days in a
OL,9,Fneonatal intensive care unit.
OL,11,FScott said he used up all his
OL,12,Fpaternity leave and then annual leave
OL,13,Fas a result, having a huge impact on
OL,14,Fhim mentally. He said had he been
OL,15,Fentitled to longer paternity leave it
OL,16,Fwould have made a massive difference:
OL,18,F"It would make a massive difference,
OL,19,Fit would make a massive difference to
OL,20,Fmums, to home life for everyone
OL,21,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
