OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,F"I struggled mentally knowing that for
OL,7,Fthe first ten days we were stuck in
OL,8,Fhospital and then when we got home I
OL,9,Fwas on countdown to going back to work.
OL,11,F"My wife was recovering from an
OL,12,Femergency c-section so I'm trying to
OL,13,Fmake sure she's okay, but then I'm
OL,14,Fhaving to go back to work because I
OL,15,Fcouldn't use anymore annual leave."
OL,17,FScott was one of several fathers
OL,18,Ftaking part in protests across the
OL,19,Fcountry on Sunday, organised by
OL,20,FTheDadShift.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
