OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,FHe hung up baby grows spelling 'two
OL,7,Fweeks isn't enough' outside the
OL,8,FToughsheet Community stadium in Bolton.
OL,10,FThere was a similar protest in
OL,11,FStockport.
OL,13,FFather-of-two Lyndon Baker said he had
OL,14,Fto get counselling after struggling
OL,15,Fwith his mental health following the
OL,16,Fbirth of his first child.
OL,18,FHe said having longer than two weeks
OL,19,Fpaternity leave would make a big
OL,20,Fdifference.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
