OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,F"More time would just give families
OL,7,Fmore of a break. I think it would ease
OL,8,Fthe anxiety, ease the pressure, and
OL,9,Fultimately help the workforce as well
OL,10,Fbecause there's going to be less
OL,11,Fpeople off for anxiety and depression
OL,12,Fas a result."
OL,14,FTheDadShift say paternity leave in the
OL,15,FUK is the worst in Europe and are
OL,16,Fcalling on the government to increase
OL,17,Fthe statutory leave.
