OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,FSunday's protest saw over 100 fathers
OL,7,Fnationwide taking part in the stunt,
OL,8,Fincluding 15 MPs, all hanging out baby
OL,9,Fgrows at more than 100 locations
OL,10,Facross the country.
OL,12,FTheir aim was to draw attention to
OL,13,Fresearch from TheDadShift and
OL,14,FMovember, showing that 45% of UK
OL,15,Ffathers experience at least two
OL,16,Fsymptoms of clinical anxiety or
OL,17,Fdepression in their baby's first year.
OL,18,FThis figure is far higher than
OL,19,Fprevious estimates, which suggested
OL,20,Fjust 10% of fathers experience
OL,21,Fperinatal depression.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
