OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,FThe polling found that nearly 1 in 15
OL,7,Fnew dads had experienced suicidal
OL,8,Fthoughts in their first year of
OL,9,Ffatherhood, and 1 in 12 reported
OL,10,Ffrightening thoughts such as
OL,11,Fdeliberately hurting their baby.
OL,13,FThe report also found that 82% of
OL,14,Ffathers believed improving paternity
OL,15,Fleave was the single biggest action
OL,16,Fthe government could take to support
OL,17,Fnew dads' mental health.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
