OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,FCampaigners said the UK's current
OL,7,Fpaternity policy was creating a mental
OL,8,Fhealth 'pressure cooker', forcing dads
OL,9,Fto return to work too early, while
OL,10,Fjuggling financial stress and
OL,11,Femotional strain, while severely sleep-
OL,12,Fdeprived.
OL,14,FAlex Lloyd Hunter, co-founder of The
OL,15,FDad Shift, said: "The UK's rubbish
OL,16,Fpaternity leave is trashing dads'
OL,17,Fmental health.
