OL,3,CFathers protest about 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cpaternity leave
OL,6,F"Without support," said Hunter, "many
OL,7,Fare left to cope alone at the exact
OL,8,Fmoment they're most vulnerable to
OL,9,Fpostpartum depression themselves."
OL,11,FAnalysis from PwC suggests better
OL,12,Fpaternity leave could prevent 500,000
OL,13,Fcases of perinatal depression over the
OL,14,Fnext 20 years, saving the NHS #1.4
OL,15,Fbillion.
OL,17,FThe Government say they are carrying
OL,18,Fout a review of wider statutory
OL,19,Fparental leave to ensure it offers the
OL,20,Fbest possible support to families..
